7696,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN3717","Title":"菏泽"}]}],"Markers":[{"Latitude":30.576279,"Longitude":104.071216,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN5101","Title":"成都 (出生地)","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"b3c9860a9dba4423914c84fbc1ff9fe4\");'><span id='b3c9860a9dba4423914c84fbc1ff9fe4_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1062&endYear=1080')\">1062-1080年</a>，0-18岁</div><div id='b3c9860a9dba4423914c84fbc1ff9fe4' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1062&endYear=1062')\">1062年</a>，出身蜀中富家。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1063&endYear=1079')\">1063-1079年</a>，在蜀中。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1080&endYear=1080')\">1080年</a>，慷慨使财，出手阔绰，磊落任气，流落市井。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"c4aa9070b5884f21883d03c2ae2a29a6\");'><span id='c4aa9070b5884f21883d03c2ae2a29a6_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年</a>，24岁</div><div id='c4aa9070b5884f21883d03c2ae2a29a6' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年</a>，匿于邻郡为园丁，因技痒难忍，题诗于亭壁，主人擅识人，认为他非此中人，赠金遣去。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":34.802941,"Longitude":114.313904,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN4102","Title":"开封","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"3a21ea070d3d4c8a91f9d25ed3aace0b\");'><span id='3a21ea070d3d4c8a91f9d25ed3aace0b_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1081&endYear=1081')\">1081年</a>，19岁</div><div id='3a21ea070d3d4c8a91f9d25ed3aace0b' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1081&endYear=1081')\">1081年</a>，折节读书，以成都第二名荐送。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"d060f44c4b23469c95cc4373691d6fe3\");'><span id='d060f44c4b23469c95cc4373691d6fe3_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1107&endYear=1108')\">1107-1108年</a>，45-46岁</div><div id='d060f44c4b23469c95cc4373691d6fe3' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1107&endYear=1107')\">1107年</a>，因告发张怀素案而立功，授供备库副使。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1108&endYear=1108')\">1108年</a>，任供备库副使。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.036519,"Longitude":120.586673,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3306","Title":"绍兴","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"efa6f5d391d446698acd276d67ce67c0\");'><span id='efa6f5d391d446698acd276d67ce67c0_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1096&endYear=1099')\">1096-1099年</a>，34-37岁</div><div id='efa6f5d391d446698acd276d67ce67c0' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1096&endYear=1096')\">1096年</a>，易容乔装为方外士，投越州知府翟思，翟思爱其书法精绝即留之。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1097&endYear=1097')\">1097年</a>，翟思之子翟汝文见他面相清炯，眸子锐烁，定非常人，又得知他习《易》、《书》，出题试之，果然经学高妙通脱，遂敬待之。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1098&endYear=1098')\">1098年</a>，翟氏归镇江，范寥安置在州学，并给其师钱百千急需，并嘱咐老师不要一次全部给他，以免他胡乱使钱。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1099&endYear=1099')\">1099年</a>，范寥离州学出游。翟思得教授书云:“自范之留，一学之士为之不宁，已付百千与之去，不知所之矣。”<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":32.064735,"Longitude":118.802891,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3201","Title":"南京","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"83f5354ca0aa4b78ba8a2828558a725f\");'><span id='83f5354ca0aa4b78ba8a2828558a725f_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1103&endYear=1103')\">1103年</a>，41岁</div><div id='83f5354ca0aa4b78ba8a2828558a725f' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1103&endYear=1103')\">1103年</a>，客居建康。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":32.195688,"Longitude":119.431494,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3211","Title":"镇江","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"49a11a9f44c74815b27343581e074d4c\");'><span id='49a11a9f44c74815b27343581e074d4c_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1104&endYear=1104')\">1104年</a>，42岁</div><div id='49a11a9f44c74815b27343581e074d4c' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1104&endYear=1104')\">1104年</a>，翟思死。范寥突然造访，嚎哭大坳于灵前，翟家为其诚意所感，厚待之。明日夙兴，范寥悄然携卷灵前黄白器皿倏逝，携之前往宜州。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"874d757e27b2416f9403c7c03772e79c\");'><span id='874d757e27b2416f9403c7c03772e79c_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1106&endYear=1106')\">1106年</a>，44岁</div><div id='874d757e27b2416f9403c7c03772e79c' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1106&endYear=1106')\">1106年</a>，无路费，至镇江府学内舍生汤东野家中，汤母给钱一万，范寥顺利到开封。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":24.491021,"Longitude":108.64309,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN451281","Title":"宜州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"add5b66bf807418a856454fa8c9f8348\");'><span id='add5b66bf807418a856454fa8c9f8348_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1105&endYear=1105')\">1105年</a>，43岁</div><div id='add5b66bf807418a856454fa8c9f8348' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1105&endYear=1105')\">1105年3月14日</a>，溯大江，历谧浦，舍舟于洞庭，取道荆湘，以趋八桂，至乙酉三月十四日，始达宜州，访黄庭坚。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1105&endYear=1105')\">1105年5月7日</a>，范寥与黄庭坚一起搬到宜州城楼上居住，终日陪侍在黄庭坚左右。<span class='label'>作品：</span>从庭坚城南晚望诗。<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">从庭坚城南晚望（宋·范寥）</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->此邦虽在牂牁南，更远不离天地间。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->人生随处皆可乐，为报中原秪如昨。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--><div class=\"footer\"><span class=\"label\">注：</span><span class=\"comment\">录自《京口耆旧传》。</span></div></div>\r\n<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1105&endYear=1105')\">1105年6月16日</a>，黄庭坚与范寥等人有龙隐洞之游。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1105&endYear=1105')\">1105年9月30日</a>，黄庭坚病逝，范寥独自为之办理后事。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":31.951147,"Longitude":119.175072,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN321183","Title":"句容","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"88ab1e3e754641cc96e4bb73a5fbd1f8\");'><span id='88ab1e3e754641cc96e4bb73a5fbd1f8_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1106&endYear=1106')\">1106年</a>，44岁</div><div id='88ab1e3e754641cc96e4bb73a5fbd1f8' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1106&endYear=1106')\">1106年</a>，又往茅山，投靠道人张怀素。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1106&endYear=1106')\">1106年</a>，张怀素与吴储、吴侔进行谋逆计划，范寥决计至京师告发张怀素。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":34.041737,"Longitude":113.858804,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN411","Title":"许昌","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"3bc8e77dcee54fcabf07cad1c0bbb7e2\");'><span id='3bc8e77dcee54fcabf07cad1c0bbb7e2_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1109&endYear=1110')\">1109-1110年</a>，47-48岁</div><div id='3bc8e77dcee54fcabf07cad1c0bbb7e2' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1109&endYear=1110')\">1109-1110年</a>，任颍昌府兵马钤辖。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":35.239435,"Longitude":115.487696,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3717","Title":"菏泽","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"f3bbe223b2244f90b6c49006e9bd3541\");'><span id='f3bbe223b2244f90b6c49006e9bd3541_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1111&endYear=1118')\">1111-1118年</a>，49-56岁</div><div id='f3bbe223b2244f90b6c49006e9bd3541' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1111&endYear=1111')\">1111年</a>，政和年间，还曾在曹州为官，吕本中有诗《次韵答曹州同官兼简范寥信中》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1112&endYear=1116')\">1112-1116年</a>，或在曹州为官。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1117&endYear=1118')\">1117-1118年</a>，不详。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":31.801003,"Longitude":119.322475,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3211 茅山","Title":"茅山"}],"Title":"范寥 <span class='inlineComment2'>(1062-1137)</span>","Detail":"<p class='inlineComment2'>引用书目：张静《黄庭坚的临终关怀者——范寥的传奇人生》　录入整理：张静</p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(0, 6, 112.3289445, 32.41973, 7)\">0-42岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(0)\">成都</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(1)\">开封</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(2)\">成都</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(3)\">绍兴</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(4)\">南京</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(5)\">镇江</a></p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(6, 12, 114.037292, 29.865228, 7)\">43-56岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(6)\">宜州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(7)\">句容</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(8)\">镇江</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(9)\">开封</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(10)\">许昌</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(11)\">菏泽</a></p>"}]}